													"type": 23,
													"value": "[Laezel] An intense, sharp pain hits Laezel's head as she struggles in the seat. Intensity:1  \"REUSE\" [Player] Please reuse  HUM_M_Rig_DFLT_CINE_MindMeldLevel_04 for the mindmeld. <Gwen Lee>"
