				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "|COM branch for Laezel interacting with the Zaith'isk. She is convinced the machine is there to cure her and refuses to open her eyes to the reality that it's killing her. The player can intervene and stop it, or let it play out. Eventually, the device explodes and the doctor calls the guards.|"
				}
